ublished audits of cultural heritage approvals linked to housing developments and introduce annual performance audits for Melbourne Water, Presutto said.\", \"from\": 9017, \"to\": 9276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9245, \"end\": 9260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne_Water\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melbourne Water\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne_Water\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne_Water\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"clear timelines\", \"from\": 9045, \"to\": 9060}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 9065, \"to\": 9070}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural heritage procedures\", \"from\": 9075, \"to\": 9103}, {\"ngram\": \"annual published audits\", \"from\": 9115, \"to\": 9138}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural heritage approvals\", \"from\": 9142, \"to\": 9169}, {\"ngram\": \"housing developments\", \"from\": 9180, \"to\": 9200}, {\"ngram\": \"annual performance audits\", \"from\": 9215, \"to\": 9240}, {\"ngram\": \"Presutto\", \"from\": 9262, \"to\": 9270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greens call for new housing minister to reopen negotiations on bills Over on X [or Twitter, if you prefer], the Greens MPMax Chandler-Matherhas called on the new housing minister to reopen negotiations with the Greens: If Labor wants their housing bills passed, I call on the new housing minister, Clare O'Neil to immediately reopen negotiations with the Greens on rent freeze/caps along with phasing out tax handouts for investors and real investment in public housing.\", \"from\": 9278, \"to\": 9750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9490, \"end\": 9496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Greens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1711374636170332e-17, \"text\": \"Greens\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Greens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Greens\"}, {\"begin\": 9502, \"e